<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/331112-going-to-read-this-book-how-is-it">Going to read this book..how is it ?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_331112'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F5900728">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/331112-going-to-read-this-book-how-is-it">7 years ago</a>
</li>
