              <span id="reviewTextContainer218028944" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13974618594908050987">I loved this early autobiography (his first 27 years). I&apos;ve loved and hated his different novels, and I understand much better now where his stories come from. The fiction is much closer to real life than I would have thought possible ... at least, if all the little anecdotes in here are true...</span>
  <span id="freeText13974618594908050987" style="display:none">I loved this early autobiography (his first 27 years). I've loved and hated his different novels, and I understand much better now where his stories come from. The fiction is much closer to real life than I would have thought possible ... at least, if all the little anecdotes in here are true...</span>
  <a data-text-id="13974618594908050987" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

